A '''knacker's yard''' is that area of a [[slaughterhouse]] where [[Body|carcasses]] unfit for [[human]] [[ingestion|consumption]] are [[Rendering (industrial)|rendered]] to useful [[material]]s such as [[glue]]. It is often used as an [[English (language)|English]] [[colloquialism]] to describe a [[person]] or object that is spent beyond all reasonable use, as in "He is only fit for the knacker's yard".

